fields.title: Perilous Height
fields.description: When enemies hit by Seismic Shock land, they take 10 damage and nearby enemies take 16 damage.

fields.title: Soaring Speed
fields.description: Landing Seismic Shock grants you a 70% Fading Haste for 2.5s.

fields.title: Dragon Mastery
fields.description: Landing Dragon Palm allows you to recast it for 1.5s.

fields.title: The Tiger and The Dragon
fields.description: Wrath of the Tiger ends with a Heavenly Strike.

fields.title: Grim Edge
fields.description: Charged Defiled Blade deals 5 bonus damage.

fields.title: Leech Blade
fields.description: Charged Defiled Blade heals you for 6 bonus health.

fields.title: Taint
fields.description: Striking a Cursed target heals you for 3 additional health.

fields.title: Wicked Strike
fields.description: The duration of Silence inflicted when hitting enemies with Defiled Blade is increased from 0.3s to 0.8s.

fields.title: Affliction
fields.description: Shadow Bolt inflicts Amplifiy, increasing all damage the target recieves by 15% for 3s.

fields.title: Agony
fields.description: Shadow Bolt deals 6 bonus damage.

fields.title: Demonic Hunt
fields.description: Sinister Strike gains 1 ability charge but cooldown increases by 2s.

fields.title: Nether Chains
fields.description: Sinister Strike inflicts Curse.

fields.title: Gorge
fields.description: Consume's cooldown is reduced by 1s. Consuming attacks further reduces cooldown by 1.5/1.0/0.5s.

fields.title: Shadow Fury
fields.description: Aborbing an attack with Consume grants Shadowbolt 2 ability charges.

fields.title: Cold Touch
fields.description: Claw of the Wicked inflicts Curse.

fields.title: Death Grip
fields.description: Landing Claw of the Wicked reduces its cooldown by 2s.

fields.title: Deaths's Embrace
fields.description: Claw of the Wicked inflicts a 1.2s Root.

fields.title: Tenacious Demon
fields.description: Claw of the Wicked drains 3 more health and range is increased by 12%.

fields.title: Hunger
fields.description: Shadow Beast pulls all nearby enemies to your position when activated.

fields.title: Shadow Prowl
fields.description: Shadow Beast increases movement speed by 35%.

fields.title: Ceremonial Spear
fields.description: Impale heals you for 2 health, and an additional 2 health for each weapon charge.

fields.title: Spear Lunge
fields.description: Increase the lunge distance of Impale by 75%.

fields.title: Thrust
fields.description: Impale deals 2 additional damage and 1 bonus damage for each weapon charge.

fields.title: Meditation
fields.description: Activating Fleetfoot near an ally heals you and your ally for 14 health each.

fields.title: Swift Feet
fields.description: Fleetfoot movement speed bonus increases to 50% from 35% and Haste effect lasts for an extra 1.5s.

fields.title: The Spear is the Way
fields.description: Spear Slash attacks during Fleetfoot grant 8% bonus energy.

fields.title: Ferocious Stance
fields.description: Increases your maximum weapon charges by 1 and blocking an attack with Kunju grants 1 weapon charge.

fields.title: Mantra
fields.description: Your next Spear Slash used after blocking and attack with Kunju heals you for 14 health.

fields.title: Poised to Strike
fields.description: Your next Spear Slash used after blocking an attack with Kunju deals 10 bonus damage.

fields.title: Dirty Tricks
fields.description: Javelin inflicts a 1.2s Root.

fields.title: Javelin Master
fields.description: Javelin deals 4 bonus damage and range is increased by 10%.

fields.title: Spear Slinger
fields.description: Javelin cooldown is reduced by 1s and hitting a wall allows you to recast Javelin for 3s.

fields.title: Whirling Blade
fields.description: Tendon Swing deals 4 additional damage and grants 15% energy when hitting at least one target.

fields.title: Spear Dance
fields.description: Whirlwind movement speed bonus increased to 50% from 20%.

fields.title: Breathe of Air
fields.description: During Haste the first hit of your Razor Boomerang heals you for 6 health.

fields.title: Cross Cut
fields.description: X-Strike deals 8 additional damage where its boomerangs intersect.

fields.title: Heavy Boomerangs
fields.description: X-Strike Stun duration increases by 0.4s.

fields.title: Surprise Attack
fields.description: X-Strike can be used while moving at 70% movement speed during Haste.

fields.title: Cold Wind
fields.description: During Haste your Razor Boomerangs inflict a 0.3s Fading Snare.

fields.title: Tailwind
fields.description: Haste increases the movement speed of nearby allies by 50% for 2s.

fields.title: Cyclone
fields.description: Enemies that are knocked into a wall by Wind Strike are Stunned for 0.8s.

fields.title: Gale
fields.description: Wind Strike spawns a gale that slows projectiles for up to 1.4s.

fields.title: Wind Fury
fields.description: Landing Wind Strike while affected by Haste reapplies Haste.

fields.title: Death Mark
fields.description: Consuming Seeker's Mark deals 4 bonus damage.

fields.title: Vortex
fields.description: Wind Bomb spawns a vortex that pulls enemies towards its center for 2s.

fields.title: Wind Stream
fields.description: Increases the duration of Wind Streams spawned by Wind Bomb by 1s. The Haste duration is increased by 1s.

fields.title: Tracking
fields.description: Each Razor Boomerang hit while mounted deals 2 bonus damage and extends the shield duration by 0.8s up to 5 times.

fields.title: Branch Out
fields.description: Root Grip range increases by 20% , drags target enemy closer and deals 4 bonus damage.

fields.title: Regrowth
fields.description: Hitting an enemy with Root Claw reduces incoming damage 10% for 2.2s, stacks up to 2 times.

fields.title: Hamstring Briars
fields.description: Thorns reduces the movement speed of the target enemy by 20%.

fields.title: Neurotoxin
fields.description: Thorns reduces the targets's damage and healing output by 20% for 2s.

fields.title: Parasitic Stems
fields.description: Thorns deals 4 bonus damage and heals you for 2 bonus health over its duration.

fields.title: Deep Burrow
fields.description: Turn Invisible during Burrow.

fields.title: Fearsome Uprootal
fields.description: Landing Burrow grants you a Shield aborning 14 damage for every target hit, lasting up to 3s.

fields.title: Impaling Roots
fields.description: Moving under an enemy during Burrow sends impaling roots upwards, dealing 10 damage to enemies struck after 0.2s delay.

fields.title: Lurker
fields.description: Burrow duration increases by 0.5s.

fields.title: Grounding Grasp
fields.description: Evil Clutch inflicts a 1s Root.

fields.title: Whiplash
fields.description: Landing Evil Clutch grants a Recast to strike nearby enemies, dealing 9 damage and inflicting Thorns.

fields.title: Creeping Roots
fields.description: Entangling Roots spreads towards nearby enemies when the effect is broken, dealing 4 damage to enemies hit, inflicting Lesser Entangling Roots.

fields.title: Sinister Sap
fields.description: Entangling Roots cooldown is reduced by 1s and deals 8 damage over its duration.

fields.title: Critical Backlash
fields.description: Barbed Husk cooldown is reduced by 2s and inflicts Thorns upon enemies hit.

fields.title: No Escape
fields.description: Burrow underground at the end of Dead Roots.

fields.title: Fervor
fields.description: Consuming Corruption increases your movement speed by 8% for 5s. Can stack up to 3 times.

fields.title: Unlimited Power
fields.description: Fading Snare duration when Corruption is consumed by Shatter is increased from 1s to 1.5s and Corruption is reapplied when consumed by Shatter.

fields.title: Devastation
fields.description: Hand of Judgement deals 3 bonus damage and hitting an enemy resets its cooldown.

fields.title: Silence
fields.description: Silence duration when Judgement is consumed is increased to 1s from 0.5s.

fields.title: Celerity
fields.description: Inhibitor's Guard increases movement speed by 25% and damage output by 15%.

fields.title: Wonder
fields.description: Inhibitors Guard absorbs 14 more damage.

fields.title: Night Stalker
fields.description: Move 16% faster when your weapon is charged.

fields.title: Reaper
fields.description: Your weapon recharges 30% faster

fields.title: Zeal
fields.description: Applying Inhibitor's Guard consumes Corruption on nearby enemies inflicting Fading Snare for 1s. The Shielded ally is healed for 8 health for each Corruption consumed.

fields.title: Return
fields.description: If Wuju is triggered you can recast it within 1.5s.

fields.title: Ruin
fields.description: Wuju inflicts Judgement on enemies struck.

fields.title: Fracture
fields.description: Ability charges of Shatter increase to 3 from 2.

fields.title: Inhibitor
fields.description: Shatter can be cast while moving at 75% speed.

fields.title: Law Bender
fields.description: When Shatter consumes Corruption or Judgement the cooldown of Inhibitors Guard is reduced by 1.5s.

fields.title: Kinetic Judgement
fields.description: Kinetic Energy inflicts Judgement.

fields.title: Absolute Power
fields.description: Powers Combined repeats itself 1 extra time.

fields.title: Synergy
fields.description: If both Judgement and Corruption are active on a target both are reapplied by Hand of Corruption/Judgement.

fields.title: Trickery
fields.description: Noxious Lunge hits reduce the cooldown of Camouflage by 1.5s.

fields.title: Spit Spit Spit
fields.description: Toxin Muck gains 1 ability charge and the cooldown is increased by 1s.

fields.title: Cut to the Chase
fields.description: Camouflage duration increased by 1s.

fields.title: Plasma Infusion
fields.description: Firing Power Blaster through a Plasma Wall increases travel distance by 25% and applies a shield aborbing 6 damage on hit.

fields.title: Power Attachment
fields.description: Charged Bolt deals 2-8 bonus damage.

fields.title: System Shock
fields.description: Charged Bolt Silence duration increases to 1.5s from 1s.

fields.title: Dispatch
fields.description: Magnetic Orb can recast to leap to a new target location knocking enemies back when you land.

fields.title: Globetrotter
fields.description: The duration of Magnetic Orb increases by 0.5s<.em> and its movement speed increases by 30%.

fields.title: Violent Revolution
fields.description: Magnetic Orb deals 6 bonus damage and knockback increases by 20%.

fields.title: Blast Processing
fields.description: Sky Strike deals 8 bonus damage and its radius is increased by 15%.

fields.title: Energy Conversion
fields.description: Sky Strike grants you a shield that absorbs 12 damage and absorbs and additional 8 damage per hit.

fields.title: Lasting Plasma
fields.description: Plasma Wall duration increases by 0.5 and cooldown is reduced by 1s.

fields.title: Plasma Booster
fields.description: Moving through a Plasma Wall increases an allied unit's movement speed by 30% for 3.5s.

fields.title: Sizzle
fields.description: An enemy passing through Plasma Wall takes 6

fields.title: Expansion Pack
fields.description: Mega Sphere cooldown is reduced by 3s and Fading Snare duration increases by 1s.

fields.title: Transformer
fields.description: Maximum amount of Pinball bounces increases by 2 and transforms you into Magnetic Orb at the end of the duration
